{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "engine_group",
      "type": "group",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1640,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 1700,
      "label": "SupplierEngine.process() — Deterministic Policy Engine"
    },
    {
      "id": "data_group",
      "type": "group",
      "styleAttributes": {},
      "x": -1560,
      "y": 920,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 2080,
      "label": "Data Sources"
    },
    {
      "id": "tools_group",
      "type": "group",
      "styleAttributes": {},
      "x": 820,
      "y": 1460,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 1000,
      "label": "Offline Calibration & Validation Tools"
    },
    {
      "id": "tool_clean",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**clean_policies.py**\nLLM-powered policy normalisation\n1. Infer schema from sample\n2. Clean each item (add machine-\n    readable fields from free text)\n3. Verify identity preserved\nUses Moonshot API",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 850,
      "y": 1500,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 220
    },
    {
      "id": "user_input",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**User Request**\nNatural language procurement request\n_e.g. \"50 laptops to Zurich, budget 100k\"_",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 120
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_parser",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Moonshot LLM Parser**\nConverts natural language → structured JSON\nModel: kimi-k2 | temp=0 | JSON response mode\nExtracts: category, quantity, budget, country, supplier preferences",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 140
    },
    {
      "id": "normalise",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Normalise Request** (`_normalise_request`)\nCity → Country resolution (Zurich → CH)\nCurrency mapping (euro → EUR) | Category L1/L2 matching\nSupplier name fuzzy lookup | UUID generation",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 140
    },
    {
      "id": "critical_check",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Missing Critical Fields?**\ncategory_l2 · country · quantity\nbudget_amount · currency",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "shape": "diamond",
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 200,
      "y": 760,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 200
    },
    {
      "id": "clarification",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Build Follow-up Question**\nGenerate targeted clarification prompt\nStore session state for next turn\nReturn `needs_clarification` status",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": -1040,
      "y": 800,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 140
    },
    {
      "id": "step1_validate",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 1: Validate Request**\nCheck: quantity present? budget present?\nDeadline in past? Tight lead time (≤5 days)?\nGenerate validation issues + ER-001 escalations",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 1680,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 140
    },
    {
      "id": "step2_filter",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 2: Filter Eligible Suppliers**\nCategory L1/L2 match → Contract active?\nService regions cover delivery country?\nData residency supported? → Policy restrictions?\nExcluded suppliers logged with reasons",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 1890,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 150
    },
    {
      "id": "step3_pricing",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 3: Attach Pricing**\nLookup by supplier × category × region × currency\nQuantity tier matching (min/max brackets)\nCH → EU fallback | CHF → EUR cross-pricing\nRe-evaluate restrictions with total value",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 2110,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 150
    },
    {
      "id": "step4_policy",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 4: Policy Evaluation**\nApproval thresholds (by currency + value band)\nPreferred supplier check (on preferred list?)\nCategory rules (security review, spec review, etc.)\nGeography rules (country-specific requirements)",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 2330,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 150
    },
    {
      "id": "step5_feasibility",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 5: Feasibility Checks**\nBudget: 20% tolerance → warning vs blocking escalation\nLead-time: all suppliers exceed deadline? → advisory\nEscalation triggers: ER-001 (input), ER-002 (preferred\nrestricted), ER-004 (no suppliers / infeasible)",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 2550,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 150
    },
    {
      "id": "step6_rank",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 6: Rank Suppliers (Weighted Scoring)**\nscore = risk × w₁ − quality × w₂ − ESG × w₃\n            − preferred × w₄ − incumbent × w₅ − mentioned × w₆\nWeights fitted via Bradley-Terry logistic regression\nLower score = better rank | Confidence % vs benchmark",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 2770,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 160
    },
    {
      "id": "step7_recommend",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 7: Build Recommendation + Audit Trail**\nPolicy trace, audit trail, supplier notes",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 140,
      "y": 3000,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 90
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome_ready",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**ready_to_award**\nNo blockers, no\napprovals needed",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": -120,
      "y": 3200,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome_pending",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**pending_approval**\nNon-blocking escalations\nrequire sign-off",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 170,
      "y": 3200,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome_clarify",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**needs_clarification**\nMissing requester input\n(ER-001 blockers)",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 460,
      "y": 3200,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome_cannot",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**cannot_proceed**\nNo suppliers or\ninfeasible (ER-004)",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 750,
      "y": 3200,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 110
    },
    {
      "id": "tool_fit",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**fit_scoring_weights.py**\nPairwise logistic regression (Bradley-Terry model)\nFeatures: price_ratio, risk, quality,\nESG, preferred, incumbent, mentioned\nOutputs normalised weights → JSON",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 850,
      "y": 1750,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 160
    },
    {
      "id": "tool_validate",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**validate_engine.py**\nCompare engine vs historical awards:\n1. Winner match (rank-1 == awarded?)\n2. Awarded supplier in shortlist?\n3. Escalation flag agreement\n4. Status vs awarded feasibility\n5. Price proximity (>15% gap?)",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 850,
      "y": 1980,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 180
    },
    {
      "id": "tool_escalation",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**escalation_stats.py**\nEscalation confusion matrix:\nTP / FP / FN / TN analysis\nPrecision, Recall, F1, Specificity\nFP breakdown by rule fired\nFN breakdown by missed target",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": 850,
      "y": 2230,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 170
    },
    {
      "id": "ds_categories",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "categories.csv\nL1/L2 taxonomy + typical units",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "shape": "database",
        "textAlign": "center"
      },
      "x": -1530,
      "y": 970,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 80
    },
